AMP Access Account

This product includes

  • No monthly fees or minimum balance
  • Eftpos and BPAY® facilities
  • The option to access additional Basic Features as an eligible government concession card holder

This product doesn't include

  • The ability to earn interest on your deposits
  • The ability to make same-day payments to an external account
  • A cheque book

A target market determination for this product is available at www.amp.com.au/bank/tmd
